<p>We welcome multiple submissions on any aspect of open education in any language. All contributions must have an open license that allows for reuse and modification, such as CC-BY. Contributions will be reviewed by the Open Education Week Planning Committee before being posted to the website. Submissions that are not appropriate for Open Education Week will not be posted.</p>
